      "E'\nLTA",
      "A DELTA AIR LINES\nThe Wide-Ride\"™ Boeing 727, Delta's major medium-range\njet has a range of over 1500 statute miles. With comfortable\nseating for 148 people, the 727 has a cruising speed of\nabout 530 miles per hour and carries a crew of three pilots\nand four flight attendants.\nPOSTCARD\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nDELTA IS READY WHEN YOU ARE!®\n0442-02628\nPrinted in U.S.A.\n2015.166.0619"
